<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Climate Solutions</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/' }) %>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="hero mb-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Explore Climate Projects</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Discover innovative solutions to climate challenges.</p>
      <a href="/solutions/projects" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">See All Projects</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card p-4 border rounded shadow">
        <img src="https://morasheatingandcooling.com/wp-content/uploads/AdobeStock_92750247-862x575.jpeg" alt="Project 1" class="mb-2" />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Energy Saver</h3>
        <p class="mb-2">Energy Saver includes projects aimed at reducing energy consumption and promoting sustainable energy use. These solutions focus on increasing the adoption of renewable energy sources (such as solar, wind, and hydroelectric power), developing energy-efficient devices and technologies, and improving energy savings in buildings and industrial facilities. The ultimate goal is to lower carbon emissions and build an environmentally friendly energy future.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="card p-4 border rounded shadow">
        <img src="https://environmentaldefence.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/iStock-1398785755-scaled.jpg" alt="Project 2" class="mb-2" />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Eco Transport</h3>
        <p class="mb-2">Eco Transport focuses on sustainable and low-emission transportation solutions that reduce environmental impact. These projects include the development of electric and hybrid vehicles, expansion of public transit systems, promotion of cycling and walking infrastructure, and innovations in clean fuels and smart mobility. The goal is to create greener cities and reduce the carbon footprint of everyday travel.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="card p-4 border rounded shadow">
        <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D12AQE6ZnAN7qP8yQ/article-cover_image-shrink_720_1280/article-cover_image-shrink_720_1280/0/1708424859023?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=IEz1JoM07H-fE27QgSw09fpNJqjp60M8nPcwdpECgYc" alt="Project 3" class="mb-2" />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Green Farming</h3>
        <p class="mb-2">Green Farming focuses on sustainable agricultural practices that protect natural resources while ensuring food security. These projects promote organic farming, efficient water usage, soil conservation, and the reduction of chemical fertilizers and pesticides. Innovations in urban farming, vertical farming, and regenerative agriculture also play a key role in building a more eco-friendly and resilient food system.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
